704
00:52:29,275 --> 00:52:31,743
Henri, stop!

705
00:52:31,811 --> 00:52:34,473
Come back! Henri!

706
00:52:43,690 --> 00:52:45,248
Oh, no.

707
00:52:50,830 --> 00:52:54,596
- Henri!
- Catherine, now that I've
told you how I feel, l...

