725
00:53:51,357 --> 00:53:54,258
- Darling? Did I say that?
- I heard you.

726
00:53:54,327 --> 00:53:56,386
It's probably fright.
It's only natural that...

727
00:53:56,462 --> 00:53:58,521
Did you mean me, Henri?

728
00:53:58,598 --> 00:54:01,431
Uh, I think I was
