- Navy.

852
01:01:39,089 --> 01:01:41,250
Oh, naval talk.
It sounds like it. Charming.

853
01:01:41,325 --> 01:01:43,520
- You make me sick.
- Good.

854
01:01:43,594 --> 01:01:45,585
Henri.

855
01:01:48,866 --> 01:01:50,857
Excuse me.

856
01:01:53,337 --> 01:01:56,397
