862
01:02:12,756 --> 01:02:15,691
I hid the papers. I knew it was
a cinch you'd change your mind.

863
01:02:15,759 --> 01:02:18,751
- You hid the papers?
- That's right. I knew I was doing you a favor.

864
01:02:18,829 --> 01:02:21,297
- You hid the papers.
